<TITLE> ETV allowed satellite transmission </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, May 29 (bdnews24.com)- The government has given Ekushey Television permission for satellite transmission, the information ministry said in a statement Tuesday. On an appeal May 24, the High Court ordered the government to permit ETV satellite transmission. The government decision was conveyed to the private TV station Tuesday. An information ministry letter said that ETV had been included afresh on the list of 12 local television channels cleared to stay on the air earlier. The issue of terrestrial transmission by Ekushey Television is still pending with the court. bdnews24
